dmca.title: Google Groups DMCA complaint - Lissa Mitchell
dmca.body:
DATE: 11-4-06
 

Google, Inc.
Attn: Google Legal Support, DMCA Complaints
1600 Amphitheatre Parkway
Mountain View, CA 94043
 

Re: Notice of Copyright Infringements by Repeat Infringer Yvonne Brownlee on the Google Group,
Plastic-Canvas-Club at: http://groups.google.com/group/PLASTIC-CANVAS-CLUB
 
Dear Sirs,
 

I am the exclusive owner of the copyrights to the following craft booklet(s) and have not granted permission for anyone to post these publicly. The copyrighted work(s) at issue are the publicly posted scans and files of my copyrighted materials as follows:
 

Fashion Doll Enchanted Train
